en_132212_0	An individual, who was in the kitchen, has died after being struck by lightning in Bulathkohupitiya police division last evening, Police Media sources stated.
en_132212_1	The deceased is a 34-year-old resident of Undugoda area.
en_132212_2	The body of the deceased is kept at the morgue of Undugoda Hospital and the post mortem examination will be conducted today, Police added.
en_132212_3	Bulathkohupitiya Police is conducting further investigations into the incident.
